<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <section id="projects">
      <h2>Projects</h2>

      <section class="project">
        <%= image_tag "picture1.jpg", alt: "E-Commerce Website" %>
        <h3>E-commerce Website Redesign</h3>
        <p>Redesigned an existing e-commerce website to improve user experience and increase conversion rates. Implemented responsive design principles to ensure a seamless experience across all devices.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Increased product search functionality with filters and sorting options.</li>
          <li>Improved checkout process with streamlined steps and clear information.</li>
          <li>Enhanced mobile responsiveness for a smooth browsing experience.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Technologies used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (jQuery)</p>
      </section>

      <section class="project">
        <%= image_tag "picture2.jpg", alt: "Social Media Website" %>
        <h3>Social Media Platform Redesign</h3>
        <p>Collaborated on a team project to redesign the user interface of a social media platform. Focused on improving user interaction and content engagement.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Implemented a new feed layout for easier content discovery.</li>
          <li>Developed interactive features for user engagement (likes, comments, shares).</li>
          <li>Integrated responsive design for optimal mobile experience.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Technologies used: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (React.js)</p>
      </section>

    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
